==Mandarin==

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: yī shēng shòu yòng bù jìn

===Idiom===
'''[[一]][[生]][[受]][[用]][[不]][[尽]]'''

# Reap the benefits of something for the rest of one's life.

#: ''[[他]][[当年]][[对]][[我]][[的]][[一番]][[教导]]，[[让]][[我]]'''一生受用不尽'''.''

